title: The dream isn’t over — AMD’s RX 7900 XTX may still hit 3GHz
description: The upcoming AMD Radeon RX 7900 XTX was initially said to have a higher clock speed. Rumors say it might still get there.

title: Great, now even the RTX 4090 power connectors are starting to melt
description: The Nvidia drama just got worse as Tom's Hardware has reported on a GeForce RTX 4090 power connector meltdown.
